When display was necessary, I **removed the `hidden-map` class** and refreshed the map. You may need to defer this operation by using `setTimeout` with a very small time.

In Gmaps:
```javascript
map.refresh();
```

Or when using google maps directly
```javascript
google.maps.event.trigger(map, 'resize');
```

